{"tid":2334820,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先買左杯天仁薑茶","createTime":"2020-12-21T11:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T14:36:11.000Z","uid":273909,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"93245e55c16b190a1be3e0737146dd8962417445","tid":2334820,"uid":273909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:36:51.000Z","msg":"話說買左杯熱既薑茶比老母<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JvwGZsc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJvwGZsc.jpg&h=4afc1035&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老母唔係好飲甜野<br />\n所以叫左不加糖<br />\n結果佢飲左啖<br />\n就話 如果唔甜就好了<br />\n我當堂呆撚左<br />\n然後跟手飲左啖<br />\n好似食緊蕃薯糖水咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n是咪要報海關<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c226658a69b9a899b58d522e00c5b0fcccb2805","tid":2334820,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T14:10:17.000Z","msg":"善破0"},{"pid":"d56b896d55925c92d9c471554f91b33235eb4581","tid":2334820,"uid":273909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c226658a69b9a899b58d522e00c5b0fcccb2805","tid":2334820,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T14:10:17.000Z","msg":"善破0"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T14:15:20.000Z","msg":"感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冬至快樂啊清"},{"pid":"339bc466d70c2c384168bee4676077bfb6af1682","tid":2334820,"uid":62260,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T14:34:28.000Z","msg":"係咪唔記得咗走甜<br />\n平時飲福圓薑奶 走甜都好好飲"},{"pid":"f97c69ff35211af4e23fb3246371c8c413f35321","tid":2334820,"uid":273909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"339bc466d70c2c384168bee4676077bfb6af1682","tid":2334820,"uid":62260,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T14:34:28.000Z","msg":"係咪唔記得咗走甜<br />\n平時飲福圓薑奶 走甜都好好飲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T14:3